Hello, thank you so much for this explanation video, it is extremely fun to watch while learning. 
I have a question regarding the % that are explained. 
The mortality rate is shown to be 5.5%, however in the breakdown of the degrees of severity, it is shown that [life threatening] is 5%. I was just wondering how do these numbers compare ?
